<p>The interesting part of Python is that this software can be used on multiple platforms, such as RStudio. This makes it more convenient and easier to use as well.</p>
<p>Python is a very functional and easy language to use once you get familar to the software.</p>
<p>Many companies use this versatile language since it is so well-structured.</p>
